              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">Lenovo is a success story of the market-based ďŹ nance of Hong Kong, not of Chinaâ&euro;&trade;s state-controlled ďŹ nancial system.

Until 2005, many of the high-tech and so-called strategic industries were declared off-limits to domestic pri- vate entry. Indigenous private entrepreneurs, many highly capable, could grow their businesses only via foreign registration.

Professor Sull chronicles seven ot...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-09-25 20:28</span>
                  
